works.description:
DUPONT is the owner of the CORIAN  
trademark, which is registered in many countries around the world  
(www.corian.com).
The blog associates the brand DALIAN to DUPONT. DUPONT has no connection  
with the DALIAN brand.
Further, the blog makes an innacurate comparison between the marks DUPONT 

CORIAN and DALIAN, stating that both products are highly similar, the only
 
difference being the price (DALIAN is more "economic").
We have received a number of complaints from customers regarding this blog
 
entry.
The blog reproduces several pictures violating copyrights.
